{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"Text zeichnen","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"\n <ol>\n  <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API\"><strong>Canvas API</strong></a></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Canvas tutorial</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_usage\">Basic usage</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_shapes\">Drawing shapes</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">Applying styles and colors</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text\">Drawing text</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">Using images</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Transformations\">Transformations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Compositing\">Compositing and clipping</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Basic_animations\">Basic animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Advanced_animations\">Advanced animations</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Pixel_manipulation_with_canvas\">Pixel manipulation</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Optimizing_canvas\">Optimizing the canvas</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Finale\">Finale</a></li>\n        </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Examples</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/A_basic_ray-caster\">A basic raycaster</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Manipulating_video_using_canvas\">Manipulating video using canvas</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details open=\"\">\n      <summary>Interfaces</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D\"><code>CanvasRenderingContext2D</code></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasGradient\"><code>CanvasGradient</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasPattern\"><code>CanvasPattern</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageBitmap\"><code>ImageBitmap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n        <li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg> <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Path2D\"><code>Path2D</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n  <li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/MDN\">Documentation:</a></strong></li>\n  <li class=\"toggle\">\n    <details>\n      <summary>Contribute</summary>\n      <ol>\n        <li><a href=\"/de/docs/MDN\">The MDN project</a></li>\n      </ol>\n    </details>\n  </li>\n </ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">« zurück</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">weiter  »</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n\n<div class=\"summary\" id=\"sect2\">\n<p>Nachdem wir im vorigen Kapitel gesehen haben, wie man <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">Gestaltung und Farben anwendet</a> , werden wir nun einen Blick darauf werfen, wie man Text auf ein <code>canvas</code> zeichnet.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"text_zeichnen","title":"Text zeichnen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Der Rendering-Kontext hält zwei Methoden zum zeichnen von Text bereit:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"filltexttext_x_y_maxwidth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/fillText\"><code>fillText(text, x, y [, maxWidth])</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Füllt einen gegebenen Text an den gegebenen (x,y)-Koordinaten. Optional mit einer maximalen Breite, die zu zeichnen ist.</dd>\n <dt id=\"stroketexttext_x_y_maxwidth_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/strokeText\"><code>strokeText(text, x, y [, maxWidth])</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Umrandet einen gegebenen Text an den gegebenen (x,y)-Koordinaten. Optional mit einer maximalen Breite, die zu zeichnen ist.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ein_filltext-beispiel","title":"ein <code>fillText</code>-Beispiel","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Der Text wird mit dem aktuellen <code>fillStyle</code> gefüllt.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">fillText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"ein fillText-Beispiel\" id=\"frame_a_filltext_example\" width=\"310\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.a_filltext_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"ein fillText-Beispiel"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ein_stroketext-beispiel","title":"ein <code>strokeText</code>-Beispiel","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Der Text wird mit dem aktuellen <code>strokeStyle</code> umrandet.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[4] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">strokeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"ein strokeText-Beispiel\" id=\"frame_a_stroketext_example\" width=\"310\" height=\"110\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.a_stroketext_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>","titleAsText":"ein strokeText-Beispiel"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"text_gestalten","title":"Text gestalten","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In den obigen Beispielen nutzen wir bereits die <code>font</code>-Eigentschaft, um den Text ein wenig größer als standardmäßig zu machen. Es gibt ein paar mehr Eigenschaften, die es erlauben, das Zeichnen von Text auf dem <code>canvas</code> zu beeinflussen:</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"font_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/font\"><code>font = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Der aktuell genutzte Text-Stil, der zum Zeichnen genutzt wird. Dieser String nutzt die selbe Syntax wie die <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS\">CSS</a> <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/CSS/font\"><code>font</code></a>-Eigenschaft. Die Standard-Schriftart ist <code>10px sans-serif</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"textalign_value\"><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textAlign\" title=\"textAlign = value\"><code>textAlign = value</code></a></dt>\n <dd>Einstellung der Text-Ausrichtung. Mögliche Werte: <code>start</code>, <code>end</code>, <code>left</code>, <code>right</code> oder <code>center</code>. Der Standard-Wert ist <code>start</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"textbaseline_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/textBaseline\"><code>textBaseline = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Baseline alignment setting. Possible values: <code>top</code>, <code>hanging</code>, <code>middle</code>, <code>alphabetic</code>, <code>ideographic</code>, <code>bottom</code>. The default value is <code>alphabetic</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"direction_value_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/direction\"><code>direction = value</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Directionality. Possible values: <code>ltr</code>, <code>rtl</code>, <code>inherit</code>. The default value is <code>inherit</code>.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>These properties might be familiar to you, if you have worked with CSS before.</p>\n\n<p>The following diagram from the&nbsp;<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/\" rel=\" noopener\">WHATWG</a> demonstrates the various baselines supported by the <code>textBaseline</code> property.<img alt=\"The top of the em square is\nroughly at the top of the glyphs in a font, the hanging baseline is\nwhere some glyphs like आ are anchored, the middle is half-way\nbetween the top of the em square and the bottom of the em square,\nthe alphabetic baseline is where characters like Á, ÿ,\nf, and Ω are anchored, the ideographic baseline is\nwhere glyphs like 私 and 達 are anchored, and the bottom\nof the em square is roughly at the bottom of the glyphs in a\nfont. The top and bottom of the bounding box can be far from these\nbaselines, due to glyphs extending far outside the em square.\" src=\"http://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/images/baselines.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"a_textbaseline_example","title":"A textBaseline example","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Edit the code below and see your changes update live in the canvas:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[2] notranslate\"><code>ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>font <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'48px serif'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textBaseline <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'hanging'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">strokeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello world'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">100</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Playable code sample\" id=\"frame_playable_code\" width=\"700\" height=\"360\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text/_sample_.playable_code.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"advanced_text_measurements","title":"Advanced text measurements","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In the case you need to obtain more details about the text, the following method allows you to measure it.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"measuretext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D/measureText\"><code>measureText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>Returns a <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextMetrics\"><code>TextMetrics</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> object containing the width, in pixels, that the specified text will be when drawn in the current text style.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>The following code snippet shows how you can measure a text and get its width.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js;highlight[3] notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">draw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ctx <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'canvas'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getContext</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'2d'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> text <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ctx<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">measureText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'foo'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// TextMetrics object</span>\n  text<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>width<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 16;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"gecko-specific_notes","title":"Gecko-specific notes","isH3":false,"content":"<p>In Gecko (the rendering engine of Firefox, Firefox OS and other Mozilla based applications), some <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CanvasRenderingContext2D#Prefixed_APIs\">prefixed APIs</a> were implemented in earlier versions to draw text on a canvas. These are now deprecated and removed, and are no longer guaranteed to work.</p>\n\n<p></p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Applying_styles_and_colors\">« zurück</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Using_images\">weiter  »</a></li>\n</ul><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Text zeichnen","id":"text_zeichnen"},{"text":"Text gestalten","id":"text_gestalten"},{"text":"Advanced text measurements","id":"advanced_text_measurements"},{"text":"Gecko-specific notes","id":"gecko-specific_notes"}],"summary":"\nNachdem wir im vorigen Kapitel gesehen haben, wie man Gestaltung und Farben anwendet , werden wir nun einen Blick darauf werfen, wie man Text auf ein canvas zeichnet.\n","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Drawing text","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Dibujar texto usando canvas","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Dessin de texte avec canvas","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"テキストの描画","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"텍스트 그리기","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Rysowanie tekstu przy użyciu canvas","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Drawing text","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Рисование текста","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"绘制文本","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"使用canvas繪製文字","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial/drawing_text","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/canvas_api/tutorial/drawing_text/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API","title":"Canvas"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial","title":"Canvas Tutorial"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/Canvas_API/Tutorial/Drawing_text","title":"Text zeichnen"}],"pageTitle":"Text zeichnen - Web API Referenz | MDN","noIndexing":false}}